Implement a class.This class is a set.

This class contains a varible n and an array a.

We need to use a[0] to a[n-1].

If the number i is in this set, a[i] should be true.Otherwise, a[i] should be false;

class Bitset {

private:
int n;
bool a[1100];
public:
Bitset() {
memset(a,0,sizeof(a));
}
void set_size(int x) {
n = x;
}
//void set(int x) ;
//void print() ;
};

Please complete this class

sample input:

2 4

1 3

sample output:

0101
